Code:
import java.util.*;
public class Main{
    public static void main(String[] args)
    {
        Scanner sc = new Scanner(System.in);
        String s = sc.nextLine();
        int i = sc.nextInt();
        String n =s.substring(0,i);
        String m= s.substring(s.length()-i,s.length());
            
        System.out.print(m+s.substring(i,s.length()-i)+n);
    }
}
Input1:
mango
2
Output1:
gonma

Input2:
mango
1
Output2:
oangm
